snippet.title: Red Dead Redemption Liars and Cheats Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Red Dead Redemption Liars and Cheats DLC Pack Official Trailer

The Liars and Cheats Pack for Red Dead Redemption features the all the new Stronghold Multiplayer Mode, Multiplayer Poker, Liar's Dice and Horse Racing - as well as the devastatingly destructive Explosive Rifle.

Platform: Microsoft Xbox 360 & Sony PlayStation 3
Made by: Rockstar Games & Rockstar San Diego ===================================

GTA Series Videos is a dedicated fan-channel keeping you up to date with all the latest news, video walkthroughs and official trailers of the most successful video games published by Rockstar Games, including Grand Theft Auto series, Red Dead Redemption, Max Payne, L.A. Noire, Bully and many others.
This channel is in no way tied to Rockstar Games or Take-Two Interactive.
